article_title: U.S. House candidates struggle to stand out
article_text:
Cheyenne, WY (82001)

Today

Partial cloudiness early, with scattered showers and thunderstorms during the afternoon. High around 60F. Winds ENE at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 50%..

Tonight

A widely scattered shower or thunderstorm is possible this evening. Then cloudy skies overnight. Low 42F. Winds N at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 30%.

article_metadata.author: Hunter Woodall, Casper Star-Tribune

og.description: CASPER – They kept saying that today was a critical day, that America was in trouble, that the world they lived in was crumbling. It was hard to stand out
